<BODY><H2> Using Modelsim on openlab
</H2> 
</font>
</center>

<p>
ssh -X username@openlab.ics.uci.edu <BR>
module load altera/modelsim/15.1 <br>
cd /pkg/altera/modelsim_ae/15.1/modelsim_ae/linux <br>
vsim <br>
</p>

<p>
Inside vsim: <br>
Create a new project <br>
Import your design files <br>
Click on compile and compile them - design before testbench <br>
Click on Simulate and use desired steps <br>
Enable Wave in View, add variable you want to track <br>
</p>

</BODY></HTML>
